{"tid":1347851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所以正義凜然嘅警察同我入黎","createTime":"2019-07-22T06:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T07:01:30.000Z","uid":136457,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d795bf6c56dc9806314856eaf5c8dd0c37881848","tid":1347851,"uid":136457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:54:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">正義之師吓話</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來所謂係學堂辛辛苦苦操完 有曬所謂記律部隊嘅訓練 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">都只不過係under黑社會 仲要幫人含到雪雪聲</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係話自己係企係正義一方咩 咩係要守護法紀咩 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原來都只係廢話 跪黑社會都跪唔切</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你因為政治立場同示威者對立 算 依家普通市民都比人打到仆街 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">原來正義之師係欺善怕惡嘅縮頭烏龜</span> 仲以為你地幾撚把炮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果操咁多年都只係幫鄉黑含撚 直接入黑社會好過啦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda4e3827fb4a509c3035ab93b04fc17f3a1dd41","tid":1347851,"uid":136457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:54:38.000Z","msg":"咁係咪姐係話撐警人士原來都撐黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1085f0889b8287c72eab21b31e464f1967b920","tid":1347851,"uid":136457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:55:09.000Z","msg":"淆底狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa2f9783e579df5b4c0ca56bc6697ab04fab0af","tid":1347851,"uid":264062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:55:35.000Z","msg":"推佢老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f3651baebd804788bcacedbcfd0e85e061999f","tid":1347851,"uid":73302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:55:57.000Z","msg":"無案底咪做警察<br />\n有案底咪做古惑仔<br />\n<br />\n都係自己人姐"},{"pid":"3a7bd8b88346181155706c5d268ed700687075fc","tid":1347851,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:56:25.000Z","msg":"警黑合作，呢個政權已經顛到放任黑社會周街打人，而警察竟然完全無動於衷，想喺社會上散佈白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n如果大家真係想反抗，要聰明啲，要智勇雙全，我知道香港好多人都係和理非，既然硬碰硬比較難做到，咁破壞香港經濟亦未嘗唔係一個好方法，破壞經濟對一個政權嚟講亦係一個毀滅性打擊，大家之前講嘅<span style=\"color: gold;\">提擠中資銀行、罷工罷市等等不合作運動</span>，其實目的都係破壞經濟<br />\n<br />\n中共作為一個極權，好多錢都會放咗喺維穏費度，既然佢都係用啲錢去對付返人民，我地亦冇必要幫佢維持經濟發展<br />\n<br />\n至於日後如果再有遊行，所有活動應該集中返喺港島，至少都要喺返各區嘅市中心，將矛頭指向政府就可以，話佢地警黑合作（要加上國際文宣），而唔係指向黑幫，有兩大原因：<br />\n<br />\n1.）會演變成群眾鬥群眾嘅局面（中共老伎倆），政府有大好良機可以化身做裁判角色，以平亂之名行維穩之實，將示威者一網打盡，運動隨之瓦解<br />\n<br />\n2.）黑幫殺人係唔眨眼，落手好狠話殺就殺，而且佢地斬死人付出嘅成本好低（揾幾個低級𡃁祭旗就可以），大家唔值得為此而博命，如果係警察無故殺人，同黑幫無故殺人，係兩種完全唔同嘅概念，前者係六四2.0，後者只係一單謀殺案，對政權嘅影響係天差地別"},{"pid":"de0a289b2a12c75844003e055f68ea1d9ccf0a91","tid":1347851,"uid":258696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:56:56.000Z","msg":"正義凜然既警察：<br />\n<br />\n沒有人 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc5b70317f3d8e8b1e1dda263815cf2f29c2e1e","tid":1347851,"uid":248470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:58:16.000Z","msg":"建制派及其政府 公然向香港市民發動恐怖襲擊！<br />\n<br />\n地鐵故意堅持開住車箱門，任由警黑合作虐打市民<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港政府= 台灣鄭捷"},{"pid":"d3c25f0a4efb49331932b5f5ad75beaffc2198e2","tid":1347851,"uid":52538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:58:28.000Z","msg":"有底薪既黑幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"423426f6881b42608a8c8ec4dc4b426c1fe7932c","tid":1347851,"uid":136457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:58:42.000Z","msg":"推到有正義之師入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ccbccdb43ae7e007de7e10e486b2c5d7b856f8c","tid":1347851,"uid":136457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:58:52.000Z","msg":"推到有正義之師入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34e2f88a04c0c860ecb79ccbfecb659b11ef984","tid":1347851,"uid":177016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:59:00.000Z","msg":"警察：因為總指揮官處理得當，黑社會社團人數得以銳減。拯救了元朗昨天受傷不敢出街的市民。"},{"pid":"462624fd227f20765e878beac2efd4008738f37f","tid":1347851,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:59:55.000Z","msg":"行古惑邊有2皮"},{"pid":"ba1b8ad97aba289c5cd4e5d800f9889958f8dcce","tid":1347851,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:00:05.000Z","msg":"黑社會：我係離撐警gar"},{"pid":"086b547a71d057c19badc0f63e3e5158e288b0ca","tid":1347851,"uid":136457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:00:36.000Z","msg":"推到有正義之師入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e7b957868eea2dc3a7ee909146d64678e03f2c","tid":1347851,"uid":136457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:01:30.000Z","msg":"自豪身份 幫人含撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}